videos.description: Khalil Tate finds Tony Ellison up the middle for a 28-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tate connects with Ellison for Arizona TD

videos.description: Arizona State's Manny Wilkins airs it out to Brandon Aiyuk to cut into the Wildcats' lead.
videos.headline: Wilkins lets it fly for 58-yard ASU TD

videos.description: Khalil Tate shows his elusiveness and finds Shawn Poindexter downfield for an Arizona touchdown.
videos.headline: Tate evades defender to throw 23-yard TD

videos.description: Eno Benjamin won't be denied as he drills the defender and pushes his way in for a touchdown.
videos.headline: Benjamin bulldozes into end zone for Arizona State score

videos.description: P.J. Johnson surges into the backfield to tackle Eno Benjamin for a safety to push Arizona's lead to 10.
videos.headline: Arizona stuffs Benjamin for safety

videos.description: Eno Benjamin follows his blockers on a touchdown run and he celebrates in the end zone.
videos.headline: Benjamin shows out after TD run

videos.description: Gary Brightwell runs for a lightning-quick 35-yard touchdown to restore Arizona's two-score lead.
videos.headline: Brightwell stuns Sun Devils with speed

videos.description: Khalil Tate jumps and throws to Tony Ellison for a touchdown to put Arizona ahead 40-24.
videos.headline: Tate channels Tebow on jump pass TD

videos.description: Manny Wilkins cuts Arizona State's deficit to one possession after keeping it himself for an 11-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Wilkins gets into the end zone untouched

videos.description: Eno Benjamin breaks through for a 22-yard touchdown late in the fourth quarter to give Arizona State a 41-40 lead over Arizona.
videos.headline: Sun Devils take late lead with 22-yard score
